	(text "output current conf (0.15V/A)\n* working range: 0.75V (5A) ~ 1.5V (10A)\nbelow 0.75V (5A):\n* output current can become unstable\n* rise time can become too small\nabove 1.5V (10A):\n* saturates at 1.5V (10A)\n\nabs max\n* clipped at 2V (clamping diode: max 500mA)\n* for input>2V, its impedance must be high\n  enough to avoid breaking clamping diode"
